  "body": "### Description\n\nCurrently, container image operations (build and push) are only supported as system properties.\r\nThis is error prone and does not provide any feedback to the user.\r\n\r\nFor example, I often do the following mistake:\r\n\r\n```\r\nmvn clean packge -Dquarkus.container-image-build=true`\r\n```\r\n\r\nand I get absolutely no feedback / idea on what  is going on and that the correct property is `quarkus.container-image.build`.\r\n\r\nExposing the operations in the cli is something that will definitely add to the experience.\r\n\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
